{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"3eccf3dfad","title":"周恩来李先念对北京市中学生两派代表的讲话","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"ccc55700d0","index":0,"year":1967,"month":8,"day":19,"articleId":"3eccf3dfad"}],"tags":[{"id":"18bf6a78fe","name":"大联合","type":"主题"},{"id":"33f01f9c5a","name":"李先念","type":"人物"},{"id":"523bb79e8f","name":"周恩来","type":"人物"},{"id":"c20d333791","name":"关键人物文稿","type":"文稿大类"},{"id":"e23dcf99fa","name":"发言","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"wenku","name":"中国文化大革命文库(第一版)","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"637e61c517","name":"李先念"}]},"publication_details":{"wenku":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"ed7b582062","type":"title","text":"周恩来李先念对北京市中学生两派代表的讲话","index":0,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"3eccf3dfad"},{"id":"2d7f51587d","type":"paragraph","text":"〖八月十九日下午，在人民大会堂揪斗谭震林大会上，周总理、李先念副总理对中学革命派代表作了重要指示。摘录如下。〗","index":1,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"3eccf3dfad"},{"id":"a7b269e640","type":"paragraph","text":"周总理说：你们43派、44派要联合起来共同对付刘邓。","index":2,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"3eccf3dfad"},{"id":"58562bd012","type":"paragraph","text":"李先念同志说：你们为什么不联合？你们对刘邓是一致的吧？你们对彭、罗、陆、杨反党集团是一致的吧？你们都是要高举毛泽东思想伟大红旗的吧？那你们为什么还不联合呢？联合起来批刘邓嘛！联合起来有力量。你们对老红卫兵要做工作。","index":3,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"3eccf3dfad"},{"id":"8c1e61c9be","type":"paragraph","text":"李先念并询问了“联动”活动情况。","index":4,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"3eccf3dfad"}],"page":{"id":"976ac2ac9c","publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"3eccf3dfad","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}